    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Registers that record the names of the deceased, date of death, and the location of their graves within a given cemetery or crypt. Occasionally additional information may be included, such as payment for the grave or associated services. When cemeteries are maintained by a church, these registers are church records.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
